(253, 'Foxcatcher', '2014-05-19', '134', '7.3', 'Steve Carell, Channing Tatum, Mark Ruffalo,', 'Bennett Miller', 'The greatest Olympic Wrestling Champion brother team joins Team Foxcatcher led by multimillionaire sponsor John E. du Pont as they train for the 1988 games in Seoul - a union that leads to unlikely circumstances.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/ae/Foxcatcher_First_Teaser_Poster.jpg/220px-Foxcatcher_First_Teaser_Poster.jpg', '15A'),
