(261, 'Walk of Shame', '2014-05-02', '95', '6.0', 'Elizabeth Banks, James Marsden, Gillian Jacobs,', 'Steven Brill', 'A reporter''s dream of becoming a news anchor is compromised after a one-night stand leaves her stranded in downtown L.A. without a phone, car, ID or money - and only 8 hours to make it to the most important job interview of her life.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bd/Walk_of_Shame_poster.jpg/220px-Walk_of_Shame_poster.jpg', 'R'),
