(282, 'Need for Speed', '2014-03-12', '130', '6.6', 'Aaron Paul, Dominic Cooper, Scott Mescudi,', 'Scott Waugh', 'Fresh from prison, a street racer who was framed by a wealthy business associate joins a cross country race with revenge in mind. His ex-partner, learning of the plan, places a massive bounty on his head as the race begins..', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e3/Need_For_Speed_poster.jpg/220px-Need_For_Speed_poster.jpg', '12A'),
