(606, 'A Haunted House', '2013-01-11', '86', '5.0', 'Marlon Wayans, Essence Atkins, Cedric the Entertainer,', 'Michael Tiddes', 'Malcolm and Kisha move into their dream home, but soon learn a demon also resides there. When Kisha becomes possessed, Malcolm - determined to keep his sex life on track - turns to a priest, a psychic, and a team of ghost-busters for help.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/00/A_Haunted_House_Poster.jpg/220px-A_Haunted_House_Poster.jpg', '18'),
(607, 'The Grandmaster', '2013-01-08', '130', '6.5', 'Tony Leung, Zhang Ziyi, Chang Chen,', 'Wong Kar-wai', 'The story of martial-arts master Ip Man, the man who trained Bruce Lee.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/23/The_Grandmaster_poster.jpg/220px-The_Grandmaster_poster.jpg', '15A'),
