(609, 'Table No. 21', '2013-01-04', '108', '7.1', 'Paresh Rawal, Rajeev Khandelwal, Tena Desae,', 'Aditya Datt', 'A couple live a mediocre life and are thrilled to have won an exotic vacation to Fiji & their excitement increases when they get a chance to play ''Tell all truth'' game for a mind boggling ...', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/27/Table_No_21_official_poster.jpg/220px-Table_No_21_official_poster.jpg', '---'),
