(640, 'Alex Cross', '2012-10-19', '101', '5.1', 'Tyler Perry, Matthew Fox,', 'Rob Cohen', 'A homicide detective is pushed to the brink of his moral and physical limits as he tangles with a ferociously skilled serial killer who specializes in torture and pain.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/03/AlexCross2012Poster.jpg/200px-AlexCross2012Poster.jpg', '15A'),
