(645, 'Lincoln', '2012-10-08', '150', '7.4', 'Daniel Day-Lewis, Sally Field, David Strathairn,', 'Steven Spielberg', 'As the Civil War continues to rage, America''s president struggles with continuing carnage on the battlefield as he fights with many inside his own cabinet on the decision to emancipate the slaves.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/6a/Lincoln_2012_Teaser_Poster.jpg/220px-Lincoln_2012_Teaser_Poster.jpg', '12A'),
