(650, 'Pitch Perfect', '2012-09-24', '112', '7.3', 'Anna Kendrick, Skylar Astin, Rebel Wilson,', 'Jason Moore', 'Beca, a freshman at Barden University, is cajoled into joining The Bellas, her school''s all-girls singing group. Injecting some much needed energy into their repertoire, The Bellas take on their male rivals in a campus competition.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b9/Pitch_Perfect_movie_poster.jpg/220px-Pitch_Perfect_movie_poster.jpg', '12A'),
