(657, 'Emperor', '2012-09-14', '105', '6.5', 'Tommy Lee Jones, Matthew Fox, Eriko Hatsune,', 'Peter Webber', 'As the Japanese surrender at the end of WWII, Gen. Fellers is tasked with deciding if Emperor Hirohito will be hanged as a war criminal. Influencing his ruling is his quest to find Aya, an exchange student he met years earlier in the U.S.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a3/Emperor_%28Film%29.jpg/220px-Emperor_%28Film%29.jpg', '12A'),
