(726, 'Men In Black 3', '2012-05-23', '106', '6.9', 'Will Smith, Tommy Lee Jones, Josh Brolin,', 'Barry Sonnenfeld', 'Agent J travels in time to M.I.B.''s early days in 1969 to stop an alien from assassinating his friend Agent K and changing history.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/8a/Men_In_Black_3.jpg/220px-Men_In_Black_3.jpg', 'PG'),
