(2132, 'Lady in the Water', '2006-07-21', '109', '5.7', 'Paul Giamatti, Bryce Dallas Howard, Bob Balaban,', 'M. Night Shyamalan', 'Apartment building superintendent Cleveland Heep rescues what he thinks is a young woman from the pool he maintains. When he discovers that she is actually a character from a bedtime story who is trying to make the journey back to her home, he works with his tenants to protect his new friend from the creatures that are determined to keep her in our world.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4f/Ladyinthewater_pos_gal.jpg/220px-Ladyinthewater_pos_gal.jpg', '12A'),
(2133, 'Clerks II', '2006-07-21', '97', '7.5', 'Brian O''Halloran, Jeff Anderson, Jason Mewes,', 'Kevin Smith', 'A calamity at Dante and Randall''s shops sends them looking for new horizons - but they ultimately settle at Mooby''s, a fictional Disney-McDonald''s-style fast-food empire.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e5/Dandrposter.jpg/215px-Dandrposter.jpg', '16'),
(2134, 'You, Me and Dupree', '2006-07-14', '109', '5.6', 'Owen Wilson, Kate Hudson, Matt Dillon,', 'Anthony Russo Joe Russo', 'A best man (Wilson) stays on as a houseguest with the newlyweds, much to the couple''s annoyance.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/79/Dupreeposter.jpg/220px-Dupreeposter.jpg', '12A'),
(2135, 'Little Man', '2006-07-14', '98', '4.2', 'Kerry Washington, John Witherspoon, Tracy Morgan,', 'Keenen Ivory Wayans', 'A wannabe dad mistakes a vertically challenged criminal on the lam as his newly adopted son.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/df/Littlemanposter.jpg/220px-Littlemanposter.jpg', '12A'),
(2136, 'Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man''s Chest', '2006-07-07', '150', '7.3', 'Johnny Depp, Orlando Bloom, Keira Knightley,', 'Gore Verbinski', 'Jack Sparrow races to recover the heart of Davy Jones to avoid enslaving his soul to Jones'' service, as other friends and foes seek the heart for their own agenda as well.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/2d/Pirates_of_the_caribbean_2_poster_b.jpg/220px-Pirates_of_the_caribbean_2_poster_b.jpg', '12A'),
(2137, 'The Devil Wears Prada', '2006-06-30', '109', '6.8', 'Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt,', 'David Frankel', 'A smart but sensible new graduate lands a job as an assistant to Miranda Priestly, the demanding editor-in-chief of a high fashion magazine.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/The_Devil_Wears_Prada_main_onesheet.jpg/220px-The_Devil_Wears_Prada_main_onesheet.jpg', 'PG'),
(2138, 'Superman Returns', '2006-06-21', '154', '6.1', 'Brandon Routh, Kate Bosworth, Kevin Spacey,', 'Bryan Singer', 'Superman reappears after a long absence, but is challenged by an old foe who uses Kryptonian technology for world domination.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/10/Superman_Returns.jpg/220px-Superman_Returns.jpg', '12A'),
(2139, 'Waist Deep', 'None', '87', '5.9', 'Tyrese Gibson, Meagan Good, Larenz Tate,', 'Vondie Curtis-Hall', 'An ex-convict (Tyrese) gets tangled up with a gang after his car is hijacked with his son inside.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/ed/Waist_Deep_%28movie_poster%29.jpg/220px-Waist_Deep_%28movie_poster%29.jpg', 'R'),
(2140, 'Click', '2006-06-23', '107', '6.4', 'Adam Sandler, Kate Beckinsale, Christopher Walken,', 'Frank Coraci', 'A workaholic architect finds a universal remote that allows him to fast-forward and rewind to different parts of his life. Complications arise when the remote starts to overrule his choices.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bd/Click_film.jpg/220px-Click_film.jpg', '12A'),
(2141, 'Nacho Libre', '2006-06-16', '92', '5.7', 'Jack Black,', 'Jared Hess', 'Berated all his life by those around him, a monk follows his dream and dons a mask to moonlight as a Luchador (Mexican wrestler).', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/35/Nachopost.jpg/220px-Nachopost.jpg', '12A'),
(2142, 'The Lake House', '2006-06-16', '105', '6.8', 'Keanu Reeves, Sandra Bullock, Dylan Walsh,', 'Alejandro Agresti', 'A lonely doctor who once occupied an unusual lakeside home begins exchanging love letters with its former resident, a frustrated architect. They must try to unravel the mystery behind their extraordinary romance before it''s too late.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bc/Poster-lakehouse.jpg/220px-Poster-lakehouse.jpg', 'PG'),
(2143, 'Garfield: A Tail of Two Kitties', '2006-06-16', '85', '5.0', 'Breckin Meyer, Jennifer Love Hewitt, Billy Connolly,', 'Tim Hill', 'Jon Arbuckle travels to the United Kingdom, and he brings his cat, Garfield, along for the trip. A case of mistaken cat identity finds Garfield ruling over a castle, but his reign is soon jeopardized by the nefarious Lord Dargis , who has designs on the estate.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d5/Garfield_A_Tail_of_Two_Kitties.jpg/220px-Garfield_A_Tail_of_Two_Kitties.jpg', 'G'),
(2144, 'The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift', '2006-06-04', '104', '5.9', 'Lucas Black, Bow Wow, Sung Kang,', 'Justin Lin', 'A teenager becomes a major competitor in the world of drift racing after moving in with his father in Tokyo to avoid a jail sentence in America.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4f/Poster_-_Fast_and_Furious_Tokyo_Drift.jpg/220px-Poster_-_Fast_and_Furious_Tokyo_Drift.jpg', '12A'),
(2145, 'A Prairie Home Companion', '2006-02-12', '106', '6.8', 'Lily Tomlin, Meryl Streep, Maya Rudolph,', 'Robert Altman Paul Thomas', 'A look at what goes on backstage during the last broadcast of America''s most celebrated radio show, where singing cowboys Dusty and Lefty, a country music siren, and a host of others hold court.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/36/Aphc_movieposter.jpg/220px-Aphc_movieposter.jpg', 'PG'),
(2146, 'Cars', '2006-06-09', '116', '7.2', 'Owen Wilson, Paul Newman, Bonnie Hunt,', 'John Lasseter', 'A hot-shot race-car named Lightning McQueen gets waylaid in Radiator Springs, where he finds the true meaning of friendship and family.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/3/34/Cars_2006.jpg/220px-Cars_2006.jpg', 'G'),
(2147, 'The Omen', '2006-06-06', '110', '5.5', 'Julia Stiles, Liev Schreiber, Mia Farrow,', 'John Moore', 'A remake of the 1976 horror classic The Omen (1976), an American official realizes that his young son may literally be the devil incarnate.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/60/The_Omen_2006_poster.gif/220px-The_Omen_2006_poster.gif', '15A'),
(2148, 'The Break-Up', '2006-06-02', '105', '5.8', 'Jennifer Aniston,', 'Peyton Reed', 'In a bid to keep their luxurious condo from their significant other, a couple''s break-up proceeds to get uglier and nastier by the moment.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/9d/Break_up.jpg/220px-Break_up.jpg', '12A'),
(2149, 'X-Men: The Last Stand', '2006-05-25', '104', '6.8', 'Hugh Jackman, Halle Berry, Ian McKellen,', 'Brett Ratner', 'When a cure is found to treat mutations, lines are drawn amongst the X-Men, led by Professor Charles Xavier, and the Brotherhood, a band of powerful mutants organized under Xavier''s former ally, Magneto.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/56/X-Men_The_Last_Stand.jpg/220px-X-Men_The_Last_Stand.jpg', '12A'),
(2150, 'See No Evil', '2006-05-19', '85', '5.1', 'Kane, Samantha Noble, Christina Vidal,', 'Gregory Dark', 'A group of delinquents are sent to clean the Blackwell Hotel. Little do they know reclusive psychopath Jacob Goodnight (Jacobs) has holed away in the rotting hotel. When one of the teens is captured, those who remain -- a group that includes the cop who put a bullet in Goodnight''s head four years ago -- band together to survive against the brutal killer.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/6f/See_no_evil.jpg/220px-See_no_evil.jpg', 'R'),
(2151, 'Over the Hedge', '2006-04-30', '83', '6.8', 'Bruce Willis, Garry Shandling, Steve Carell,', 'Tim Johnson Karey Kirkpat', 'A scheming raccoon fools a mismatched family of forest creatures into helping him repay a debt of food, by invading the new suburban sprawl that popped up while they were hibernating...and learns a lesson about family himself.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f7/Over_the_Hedge_Poster.jpg/220px-Over_the_Hedge_Poster.jpg', 'G'),
(2152, 'The Da Vinci Code', '2006-05-19', '146', '6.5', 'Tom Hanks, Audrey Tautou, Ian McKellen,', 'Ron Howard', 'A murder inside the Louvre and clues in Da Vinci paintings lead to the discovery of a religious mystery protected by a secret society for two thousand years -- which could shake the foundations of Christianity.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e9/The_da_vinci_code_final.jpg/220px-The_da_vinci_code_final.jpg', '15A'),
(2153, 'Poseidon', '2006-05-06', '98', '5.6', 'Kurt Russell, Josh Lucas, Richard Dreyfuss,', 'Wolfgang Petersen', 'On New Year''s Eve, the luxury ocean liner, Poseidon, capsizes after being swamped by a rogue wave. The survivors are left to fight for survival as they attempt to escape the sinking ship.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/84/Poseidon_%282006%29_film_poster.jpg/220px-Poseidon_%282006%29_film_poster.jpg', '12A'),
(2154, 'Just My Luck', '2006-05-12', '108', '5.3', 'Lindsay Lohan, Chris Pine, Faizon Love,', 'Donald Petrie', 'Manhattanite Ashley is known to many as the luckiest woman around. After a chance encounter with a down-and-out young man, however, she realizes that she''s swapped her fortune for his.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/ba/Justmyluck.jpg/220px-Justmyluck.jpg', 'PG'),
(2155, 'Goal!: The Dream Begins', 'None', '118', '6.8', 'Kuno Becker, Alessandro Nivola, Marcel Iures,', 'Danny Cannon', 'The extremely talented Santiago Munez is given a chance at professional football, after being spotted by a scout who has ties with Newcastle United.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/96/GoalPoster.jpg/220px-GoalPoster.jpg', 'PG'),
(2156, 'Mission: Impossible III', '2006-05-05', '125', '6.8', 'Philip Seymour Hoffman, Ving Rhames, Billy Crudup,', 'J.J. Abrams', 'Ethan Hunt comes face to face with a dangerous and sadistic arms dealer while trying to keep his identity secret in order to protect his girlfriend.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bc/Mission_Impossible_III.jpg/220px-Mission_Impossible_III.jpg', '12A');
