(2157, 'Hoot', '2006-05-05', '91', '5.6', 'Luke Wilson, Logan Lerman, Brie Larson,', 'Wil Shriner', 'A young man (Lerman) moves from Montana to Florida with his family, where he''s compelled to engage in a fight to protect a population of endangered owls.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/6d/Hoot_film.jpg/220px-Hoot_film.jpg', 'PG'),
