(2430, 'Alien vs. Predator', '2004-08-12', '101', '5.6', 'Sanaa Lathan, Lance Henriksen, Raoul Bova,', 'Paul W. S. Anderson', 'During an archaeological expedition on Bouvetya Island in Antarctica, a team of archaeologists and other scientists find themselves caught up in a battle between the two legends. Soon, the team realize that only one species can win.', 'http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f7/Avpmovie.jpg/220px-Avpmovie.jpg', '15'),
